#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
Cybersecurity Scholarship + Grant Finder (MVP)

Features:
- Scans 50+ non-traditional sources (gov, libraries, nonprofits, industry groups, conferences, companies)
- Checks robots.txt before crawling any URL
- Builds/updates a local SQLite database of opportunities
- Supports user profiles (name, GPA, state)
- Matches opportunities to user profile eligibility hints
- Dynamic CLI with ASCII art banner and simple menu
"""

